sentences.english: This picture shows Allied troops waiting for evacuation from the beaches at Dunkirk.
sentences.chinese: 這張照片顯示盟軍準備從敦刻爾克的灘頭撤退。

sentences.english: This picture shows how complex the evacuation from Dunkirk could be.
sentences.chinese: 這張照片顯示了敦刻爾克撤退的複雜程度。

sentences.english: They sailed back to Britain from the French town of Dunkirk.
sentences.chinese: 他們乘船回英國從敦刻爾克法國小鎮。
